headline: Northwest Middle School Unveils New Weight Room in Partnership with Elevance Health and Impact Fitness Foundation
summary: INDIANAPOLIS, September 24, 2025--Indianapolis Public Schools' Northwest Middle School today celebrated the unveiling of its newly transformed weight room, a project made possible through a partnership with Elevance Health and the Impact Fitness Foundation (IFF).
